This query will return an array of `TonicEstimateRevenue` objects that match the specified date. Each object will have an `estimates` field that contains an array of the related `estimates` for that specific date.

Note that the specific structure of the returned `result` will depend on your data model and relationships. You would need to define the appropriate relationships in your Prisma schema for the associated models/entities to be included in the query results.

